{"tid":1926834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"死啦!有冇人同我一樣好驚23條...","createTime":"2020-03-15T11:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T02:15:40.000Z","uid":283912,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc40f3981ad9551d25545a1adf8f5c71626e18a","tid":1926834,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>好驚佢唔即刻搞阿</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n何妖呢條助攻皇根本就靠害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候推23條完全係送奶共派九月去死<br />\n777派成萬蚊先勉強攞返幾分民望<br />\n如果依家政府宣布立23條同自殺冇分別<br />\n我係驚佢唔夠膽跟隊炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我哋要啟動文宣機器幫手一齊煲大佢<br />\n<br />\n1️⃣等淺色中立港豬重拾送中恐慌<br />\n就黎反送中一週年,係時候蘊釀返抗爭情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2️⃣藍營加速主義,迫奶共派/偽中立/淺藍表態<br />\n邊個唔支持/唔堅定就係偽藍扮藍唔夠藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3️⃣加速社會邊緣化藍屍,將藍屍同23條劃上等號<br />\n再加強宣傳藍暴,斬人,開車撞人,劏肚之類暴行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4️⃣送埋最尾一粒子彈俾美國郁關係法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一齊同何妖講聲多謝就去開工喇</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec0eefbc8425df1a95901d659e085035c298436","tid":1926834,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T11:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M2XZkbC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM2XZkbC.jpg&h=983e51ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日悼念梁烈士，現場10人都無，手足嚟緊？"